title: Residents of Keumbu market in Kisii town share their remarks of the Jubilee leadership - VIDEO | The Standard
text:
KTN Prime / 1 day ago [VIDEO] Residents of Keumbu market in Kisii town share their remarks of the Jubilee leadership 
The best way to judge Kenya’s economic pulse under the jubilee leadership is undoubtedly in the market place where ordinary Kenyans buy and sell on a daily basis. It is a melting pot that brings together the retailers of agricultural and industrial produce impacted by everything from taxes to the climate. KTN’s Fred Moturi spent the day with traders at Keumbu market in Kisii and now brings us their take on this election. Related Videos
